Number 2

Algorithm for a student crossing the road with Decision and repetition steps e.g (if/else  loop)

Step1- Student Standing by the road
Step2- Student is waiting to cross the road
Step3- Student is checking the traffic signs
Step4- Traffic Sign is on Green
Step5- While traffic sign is yet to turn red, Student continue waiting ( repetition/Loop)
Step6- (if/else Condition): if the traffic sign is Red, student cross the road
                            else student will wait
Step7- Traffic sign turns Green
Step8- The road is safe for student to cross
Step9- Student cross the road

                            

